					<h1 class="entry-title">Rare Earth Metal Overview</h1>
					<p class="headline_meta">by <span class="author vcard"><span class="fn">Casey Research</span></span> on <abbr class="published" title="2009-10-02">October 2, 2009</abbr> &middot; <span><a href="http://www.runtogold.com/2009/10/rare-earth-metal-overview/#comments" rel="nofollow">1 comment</a></span></p>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text entry-content">
